EN: This concert is an appropriate environment for us to relax.

ZH: 规定每天适当的阅读时间对培养孩子的阅读习惯很重要。
EN: Setting aside an appropriate reading time every day is crucial for cultivating a child's reading habits.

ZH: 这个笑话是适当的，我们都笑开了。
EN: That joke was appropriate, and we all laughed.

